{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhopkondq3k0","created":1775746431078,"text":"社会知觉"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhopmtcr3g80","created":1775746598047,"text":"社会知觉的概念"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhopo7osw5c0","created":1775746707615,"text":"定义"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhopr5js61c0","created":1775746938050,"text":"指人对【社会性的】人和事物【形成】的整体性的印象，\n对【各种担负社会角色并具有个性色彩的】人，\n或是人与人之间的关系或对群体所建立的\n最初印象和概念。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhopo9ojmag0","created":1775746711953,"text":"分类"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhopwtfs2jc0","created":1775747381872,"text":"3类知觉；自我知觉理论（贝姆）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhopx1os9cw0","created":1775747399831,"text":"自我"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhopxty437k0","created":1775747461345,"text":"自我价值定向理论：人具有解释自我的基本需求"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhopx63k44o0","created":1775747409431,"text":"他人"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhopx7fqmug0","created":1775747412344,"text":"人际"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhopobbrgeo0","created":1775746715534,"text":"一些相关概念"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhopygym60o0","created":1775747511441,"text":"印象"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhopyl9rixs0","created":1775747520822,"text":"是社会知觉的结果；过程与结果的关系"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhopye6y5bk0","created":1775747505414,"text":"一般知觉"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoq1h14yjs0","created":1775747746687,"text":"主要指对【物】的物理特性，时间，运动等的关注"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhopyg56zz40","created":1775747509662,"text":"社会认知"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhopyok2dg00","created":1775747527975,"text":"是…的上位概念；社会知觉是社会认知的一个环节"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhopyht5k1k0","created":1775747513288,"text":"社会推理(?)"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoq4r5azps0","created":1775748003798,"text":"也是社会认知的一个环节，涉及到加工、解释、判断，结果是社会判断，和社会知觉同级。"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhopn61rttc0","created":1775746625681,"text":"知觉输入的结果：印象"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoposcrt9c0","created":1775746752600,"text":"定义"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhopoujvmsg0","created":1775746757383,"text":"性质"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhor3gj68ig0","created":1775750723438,"text":"间接性、固执性、综合性"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhopoyloadc0","created":1775746766199,"text":"形成模式"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhopp2a4sm80","created":1775746774208,"text":"信息选择倾向"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhopn8z6qew0","created":1775746632055,"text":"有目的的偏差：认知偏差"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhopnc60vnk0","created":1775746638999,"text":"从输入到输出：印象管理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhopnfxs4ps0","created":1775746647208,"text":"认知的视角：内隐认知"},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}